HEADWORD: Hereof
<hw>Here*of"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Of this; concerning
this; from this; hence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Hereof</qex> comes it that Prince Harry is valiant.</q>
